data.description: Beautiful 5 BR/2.5 BA home on a quiet street in the peaceful Lakewood Links Golfing Community (one of the BRs would be a great office space) . This home features an open split floorplan w/hardwood flooring, Granite Countertops , Eat-in kitchen w/custom  cabinetry, separate formal dining area, a combination of trey and cathedral ceilings, Custom built wall shelves accenting the great/living room fireplace, Jack & Jill Bathroom w/tile floor. The large master suite features his and her closets, separate vanities, garden tub, stand up shower and tile flooring.  Escape to the back covered porch overlooking a spacious yard with irrigation system, mature trees, and a view of the 10th green.  Sellers willing to pay a portion of Buyer closing costs or a 1 year rate buy down with acceptable offer.
